commits.sourceNew:
/** * Returns the identifier of this {@link Sorter}. *

This identifier is similar to {@link Object#hashCode()} and should be * chosen so that two instances of this class that sort documents likewise * will have the same identifier. On the contrary, this identifier should be * different on different {@link Sorter sorters}. */ public abstract String getID();
